Reality / Inputs
      ↓
[ BLP ]   (binding / relationships)
      ↓
[ CE ]    (conversion / transformation)
      ↓
[ CMP ]   (market / value flow)
      ↓
[ UICL ]  (identity + credit + trust)
      ↓
Sustained System / Economy

(UICL sits across all layers as a persistent substrate)

